OL,5, Culture Secretary Nadine Dorries has   
OL,6, confirmed the BBC licence fee is to be 
OL,7, frozen at #159 for two years.          
OL,9,FSpeaking in the House of Commons on    
OL,10,FMonday, Ms Dorries said the government 
OL,11,Fcould "not justify extra pressure on   
OL,12,Fthe wallets of hardworking households".
OL,14,FFollowing the two-year freeze, she said
OL,15,Fthe fee will rise in line with         
OL,16,Finflation for the following four years.
OL,18,FDirector general Tim Davie said the    
OL,19,Ffreeze would mean "tougher choices     
OL,20,Fwhich will impact licence fee payers". 
